{"tid":995258,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Netflix 傳出將製作《Resident Evil》劇集","createTime":"2019-01-25T09:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T12:52:16.000Z","uid":41343,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ead6df268e815915e00aa168105c5bd2763ead76","tid":995258,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T09:57:00.000Z","msg":"由人氣電玩改編的《Resident Evil》電影系列在去年正式確立重啓，將忠實於電玩中的恐怖氛圍，而非過去導演 Paul Anderson 強調的動作風格，更將以《Resident Evil 7》作為基礎打造，可惜原本的製作人溫子仁（James Wan）於先前專訪中，澄清了他已不是該團隊人員，實為可惜。<br />\n<br />\n而就在電玩《Resident Evil 2》重製版推出在即前夕，根據 Collider 最新情報指出，Netflix 將與 Constantin Film 合作打造《Resident Evil》最新影集系列，共同探索 Umbrella Corporation 的內部運作、T 病毒爆發後的社會新秩序。現已找來同步執行《Resident Evil》重啟電影的 Johannes Roberts 編寫劇本，此操作或將協助兩部作品達到電影宇宙的擴張。"},{"pid":"a31c0a54bff7601013d2081c3aae6924bb9538b0","tid":995258,"uid":186323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T10:16:47.000Z","msg":"Ada wong搵邊個先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96deb299149116318bc3767cb1e5b0b4134f1ba5","tid":995258,"uid":165361,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a31c0a54bff7601013d2081c3aae6924bb9538b0","tid":995258,"uid":186323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T10:16:47.000Z","msg":"Ada wong搵邊個先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T12:41:37.000Z","msg":"唔好景甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1290b691733a48497aa9efd40acb05bf7ac55a47","tid":995258,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T12:46:31.000Z","msg":"唉Netflix<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b4d0cf59225609e71ea3c63915018ad019ed46","tid":995258,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a31c0a54bff7601013d2081c3aae6924bb9538b0","tid":995258,"uid":186323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019